    public abstract class TDynaViewCrudBaseBehavior<M extends TModelView,​E extends org.tedros.server.model.ITModel>
extends TDynaViewSimpleBaseBehavior<M,​E>
    The basic behavior of the CRUD view. This behavior is applied on view and entity that need to access the business layer on the application server. For entity processing use TEjbService or TEntityProcess in the TEntityModelView.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
